channel.title: Getting a Server Online
channel.description: I need some help getting my server online, I had a server running 3-4 years ago when I was using Windows XP. Now im using Windows 7 and im having way more difficulties with runserver.bat, compile.bat, and getting my IP to work. I have the Latest JDk and JRe Installed on my computer already. I haven't Portforwarded either. I have my environmental variables set up also. Can anyone help me via TeamViewer?
